channel.title: Quiting Coding For Now
channel.description:
Most of you know me from IntrepidScape that I released not too long ago. I am deciding to take a break from coding and just help people out on the forums. It was a hard decision that I had to make and it took me a while to finally choose what I was going to do. I know that this is probably not a big deal to most of you because I'm not very popular in the world of MoparScape coding. If you ever played IntrepidScape, you knew that I worked hard at what I did. This dosen't mean that I'm quiting coding forever, I am only taking a break. I'll be back coding in about three months.
BTW If you don't know who I am, don't give negative feedback!
Thanks, Maxxy AKA Mod Intrepid
